              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">怪笑猫猫帽</span>，累积1层<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">隐具余数</span>。</p><p>如果本角色生命值至少为6，则对自身造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/67d6f9d70e695a791caa42953d11e1e3_1656237069515075937.png",
