                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">怪笑猫猫帽</span>，累积1层<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">隐具余数</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/1f6d82b825fc55a454fe56d6bb68239e_7563075068463976077.png",
